org.anchoranalysis.core.identifier.provider

Class NameValueMap<T>

  • Object
    • NameValueMap<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - element-type in NameValue instances.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<NameValue<T>>, NamedProvider<T>

    public class NameValueMap<T>
extends Object
implements Iterable<NameValue<T>>, NamedProvider<T>
    Builds a mapping from names to values, given NameValue instances.

    Each name in NameValue should be unique.

    This is similar as a standard Map but additionally:

    • iteration provides NameValue elements.
    • it exposes itself as a NamedProvider.
    Author:
    Owen Feehan
